headline: Is Broadcom Stock a Buy Now?
summary: Investors looking for artificial intelligence (AI) stocks have plenty of options.  Broadcom (NASDAQ: AVGO) is one of the tech companies that is a unique play in the artificial intelligence market and could be a good long-term investment.  One of Broadcom's biggest opportunities comes from its application-specific integrated circuits (ASICs) that are used in AI data center infrastructure.
